[0.017, "o", "\u001b[5A\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[1;38;5;117m●\u001b[0m To be precise: do you want me to **stop** myself (pausable, can be restarted) or **remove** myself entirely (gone, would need `otters run` to recreate)?\r\n\r\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[38;5;244m─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;38;5;213m›\u001b[0m \u001b[38;5;240mm\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;240message the agent — / for commands, ? for help\u001b[0m                                                                                            \u001b[K\r\n\u001b[38;5;244m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"]
